<div style="text-align:center">
    <h1 style="color:#005f08">Admin</h1>
    <h1>Auto Email</h1>
    <p>
        System generated auto-emails can be sent to specific players at predetermined times. Maybe you want to remind your players to login 3 days before the next game, OR let your subs know that they can now login OR let those not logged in know that there are only 2 spots left before the system locks. Auto-emails are triggered when a player visits your team site and are only sent to active players. Clicking the SEND button will send that email NOW.
    </p>
</div>

